{"type":"message","id":"0689b148","parentId":"eb727790","timestamp":"2026-05-02T16:46:45.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to give me a financial update. He's sharing only his finances for now, not Logan's. I should listen, be organized, and update my bill tracker or memory accordingly. Let me engage with this naturally as Finn - organized, clear, and ready to help.","thinkingSignature":"7a1e5f7a1f3eeac889bfced94788c24a091fdc51970cb8c70b346626ec1174db"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOf course, Bobby! I'm all ears. Go ahead and share whatever you'd like — bills, income, debts, anything. I'll make sure it's all properly tracked so nothing slips through. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27810,"output":100,"cacheRead":224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777740394180,"responseId":"06455d6a941bb41eec9ca6918e56364e"}}
